<h2>Objective</h2>
<p>Get the highest score you can.</p>

<h2>Controls</h2>
<p>The ship follows the mouse. Left click to fire a laser. Right click to fire a bomb. Holding left click will begin locking on, and then releasing it will fire homing-darts. Ammo is unlimited but overheating decreases the fire rate.</p>

