<dl class="dl-horizontal">
  <dt>Fighter <small>(1 point)</small></dt>
  <dd>The most basic unit, these aren't the brightest pilots. Move towards you and shoot! Move towards you and shoot! Barely a step up from space invaders intelligence.</dd>
  <dt>Kamikaze <small>(2 points)</small></dt>
  <dd>These pilots have nothing to lose. Strapped into a ship without weapons, all they can do is slowly drift forwards until they spot an enemy to run into.</dd>
  <dt>Bomber <small>(5 points)</small></dt>
  <dd>Why aim when you have explosives? Bombers meander across the battlefield dropping bombs and hoping they hit something.</dd>
  <dt>Spinner <small>(10 points)</small></dt>
  <dd>Aerodynamics mean nothing in space, but that doesn't make these spinning ships any less ridiculous to look at.</dd>

</dl>
